plot: Nombre Original: DeadwalkersDirector: Spencer EstabrooksActores: Michael Sheperd     Adam Sterling     Brendan Hunter     Lisa Marie Digiacinto     Cheryl Hanley     Dale Buchananounty hunter and gunman Jack Link has a knack for trouble, but when he stumbles into a town cursed with the undead, he might have bit off more than he can chew. Can he and his unlikely allies break the curse and make it out alive or will the evil in the old west consume them all? Explicit.
